headline: Q4 Industrial Packaging Earnings: Ball (NYSE:BALL) Impresses
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how industrial packaging stocks fared in Q4, starting with Ball (NYSE:BALL).
